snippet.title: Baby Adam's 1st Birthday - Kids Birthday party!
snippet.description:
Baby Adam's 1st Birthday - Kids Birthday party!

Celebrate Baby Adam's 1st birthday with Diana and Roma"s Family! Watch as we throw a fun and adorable party filled with decorations, games and a huge birthday cake! This video is sure to make you smile and give you some ideas for your own little one's special day!
